name: Stick Up (DallaswithaD)
description:
Created for West Jam 6, a local game jam in Brandon, MB.

Build Your Way Out, and stick falling debris to jump off of, and get as high as you can!

How To Play: 

     WASD - Move

     Space - Jump (Hold for more air!)

     Left Click - Fire Left Gun

     Right Click - Fire Right Gun

     Shift - Fast Drop

Made By:

Development - Dallas Flett-Wapash

VO / Sound FX - Colton Smith

3D Models (Character, Background) - Swift
